ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This Java console application simulates a traffic inspection system that analyzes riders for common traffic rule violations.
It processes data for 10 riders, checks eligibility based on age, helmet usage, and license possession, and generates a final violation report.

The project focuses on looping concepts, conditional logic, counters, and real-world problem solving.

ğŸš€ Features

Checks rider eligibility based on age

Identifies underage riders

Detects helmet violations

Detects license violations

Uses counters to generate a summary report

Skips unnecessary checks using continue

