ğŸ§  Program Logic

The program loops through 10 riders

For each rider:

Checks if the rider is under 18

If yes, marks as underage and skips further checks

Checks helmet usage

Checks license availability

Counts violations separately

Displays a final report showing:

Total underage riders

Helmet fine count

License fine count
